
Ranger Help for: ride
=====================

SYNTAX:      ride <garou target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   4
BASE SP:     65 sp
SKILL TYPE:  aid

SUMMARY:    
This skills allows a Ranger and a willing garou(in wolf form) to
become allies. The Ranger rides and fights on the Garou's back.
More to come on this one.

